    "Walter Brueggemann, Warren Carter": "An Obedient, Devouring Lion, 13:20-25\nThe deception of",
    "John Trapp": "Lay my bones beside his bones. ] So David `[char_David_Rut_4]` Pareus would be buried in the same sepulchre wherein were laid up the bones of his master Hier. Zanchius, A.D. 1591. { a } { a } Parei vita operibus praefixa.\nVer.\n31. Lay my bones beside his bones.] So David `[char_David_Rut_4]` Pareus would be buried in the same sepulchre wherein were laid up the bones of his master Hier. Zanchius, A.D. 1591. {a} {a} Parei vita operibus praefixa.\nVer."
